tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE MachineLearningModels (
    model_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_name VARCHAR(255),
    model_description TEXT,
    model_type VARCHAR(50),
    model_accuracy DECIMAL(5,2),
    training_data_size INT,
    training_time TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE machine_learning_models (
  model_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  model_name TEXT NOT NULL,
  model_description TEXT,
  algorithm TEXT NOT NULL,
  accuracy FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE training_data (
  data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  model_id INT NOT NULL,
  data_input TEXT NOT NULL,
  data_output TEXT NOT NULL,
  data_accuracy FLOAT,
  FOREIGN KEY (model_id) REFERENCES machine_learning_models(model_id)
);

CREATE TABLE hyperparameters (
  parameter_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  model_id INT NOT NULL,
  parameter_name TEXT NOT NULL,
  parameter_value TEXT NOT NULL,
  FOREIGN KEY (model_id) REFERENCES machine_learning_models(model_id)
);

CREATE TABLE evaluation_metrics (
  eval_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  model_id INT NOT NULL,
  metric_name TEXT NOT NULL,
  metric_value FLOAT NOT NULL,
  FOREIGN KEY (model_id) REFERENCES machine_learning_models(model_id)
);

CREATE TABLE predictions (
  prediction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  model_id INT NOT NULL,
  prediction_input TEXT NOT NULL,
  prediction_output TEXT NOT NULL,
  prediction_accuracy FLOAT,
  FOREIGN KEY (model_id) REFERENCES machine_learning_models(model_id)
);
